Package commands

package commands
Commands package is a package that contains all command classes.
  • Class
    Description
    AbstractCommand
    The AbstractCommand class is an abstract class that implements the ICommand interface.
    AddElementCommand
    Command for adding an element to collection from user input.
    AddIfMaxCommand
    Command for adding element to collection if its value is more than max in the collection.
    ExecuteScriptCommand
    Command for executing a script from a txt file.
    ExitCommand
     
    FilterByChapterCommand
    Shows filtered collection by chapter.
    FilterLessThanHealthCommand
    Shows filtered collection by less health.
    HelpCommand
    Command that shows usage and description of all available commands.
    ICommand
    Interface for all commands.
    InfoCommand
    Command that show information about collection.
    PrintUniqueHeartCountCommand
    Shows space marines with unique heart count.
    RemoveAtCommand
    Command that removes element at given index.
    RemoveByIdCommand
    Command that removes element from collection with given id.
    RemoveGreaterCommand
    Command that removes all elements greater than inputted.
    SaveCommand
    Command that saves collection to a csv file.
    ShowCommand
    Command that displays collection elements for user.
    UpdateByIdCommand
    Command that updates element by id from user input.
